code: @Override public Processor createProcessor(RouteContext routeContext) throws Exception {     ObjectHelper.notNull(definition.getPattern(), "patterns", this).     if (definition.getExcludePatterns() != null) {         return new RemovePropertiesProcessor(definition.getPattern(), definition.getExcludePatterns()).     } else if (definition.getExcludePattern() != null) {         return new RemovePropertiesProcessor(definition.getPattern(), new String[] { definition.getExcludePattern() }).     } else {         return new RemovePropertiesProcessor(definition.getPattern(), null).     } }
